{"tid":2513314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個同女同學有身體接觸嘅經歷","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T01:06:23.000Z","uid":11127,"like":69,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec8dce63f01da2ae77998435114486414f3649f","tid":2513314,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"有次lunch同啲friend喺學校吹水等位<br />\n就成棚人堆咗喺個通道嗰度啦<br />\n傾傾吓計 突然後面唔知乜水叫我個名<br />\n我嗰陣諗住誇張啲應佢<br />\n所以好大動作轉身 隻右手fag出去咁樣<br />\n點知一轉身大叫：「邊個！」嘅同時<br />\n成隻手打咗落後面經過個女同學對波度<br />\n我即刻呆咗望住佢 又掃視咗佢個胸幾秒<br />\n佢mark大個口停咗喺度 大家你眼望我眼<br />\n之後我尷尬笑咗一笑即刻擰轉身<br />\n跟住後尾再同個女同學講嘢都冇咩特別<br />\n唔知佢記唔記得呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2962a4a7bacaf7def9894c4117d6e4add0702820","tid":2513314,"uid":353080,"like":11,"dislike":35,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"同男朋友互射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0093f955afd010c651956f99d8cb138398ae9da5","tid":2513314,"uid":79793,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"媾左條女番黎交配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f8085267f77066849bc937f7d9849415fb30ee","tid":2513314,"uid":214384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"同女同學小息玩攬攬"},{"pid":"262231567936f9dc782dbc9b4edd6dd146910194","tid":2513314,"uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":75,"score":-70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a355d9935c28ebd6f0599ddf551fe727819a7e7","tid":2513314,"uid":55458,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"一野揸落女同學個波度<br />\n結果俾人捉咗入男童院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭髮都俾人